CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:987189
DTSTAMP:20260314T201151Z
DTSTART:20260327T233000Z
DTEND:20260328T015000Z
SUMMARY:Beaches, A New Musical
LOCATION:Majestic Theatre, 245 West 44th St, New York NY 10036
DESCRIPTION:<p><em>Beaches, A New Musical</em>, based on the best-selling
  novel that became the blockbuster film, brings to the stage one of the
  most iconic friendships in popular culture. This sweeping, emotional, and
  joy-filled new musical follows the vivacious Cee Cee and elegant Bertie,
  who meet as children and become fast friends. From pen-pals to roommates
  to romantic rivals, Cee Cee and Bertie&rsquo;s oil-and-water friendship
  perseveres over the course of 30 years through even the most tragic
  trials. With a touching vulnerability, <em>Beaches</em> exemplifies the
  triumph of the human spirit and the bonds of friendship.</p>
END:VEVENT
